# Storybook Rules

## Meta

```ts
const meta = {
  title: "Category/ComponentName",
  component: Component,
  tags: ["autodocs"],
  args: { ...defaults },
  argTypes: ...
};
```

## ArgTypes

- `control`: "select" | "boolean" | "text"
- `options`: variant/size/intent arrays
- `description`: field description
- `table`: `type: { summary: "TypeName" }`, `defaultValue: { summary: "value" }`

## Stories

- Default, per Variant, per Size, per Intent stories
- Use `render` function for custom rendering
